{
  "description": "3D single-hero survival board FRAME: composes hero-nav (units + move budget as energy) + gather (wood/stone resource nodes) + fx-particles + survival-flow (build-camp win / energy-out loss) onto one shared GameState with a single render authority. Games consume this molecule and supply only theme/assets/units/tiles/features/camp thresholds via config.",
